summary: This ENB has natural bright colors and sharp visuals. I'm using CoT and ELFX but should work fine with or without it.
descriptionHtml:
This ENB has natural bright colors and sharp visuals. I'm using CoT and ELFX but should work fine with or without it.


[b][center]Installation[/center][/b]

- Download the lates ENB files by Boris Vorontsov and install it
- Download the ENB files and copy them in your skyrim folder
